  "admissionRequirementsRtf": "<h3>Admission requirements</h3> <p>For information on admission requirements, refer to the <a href=\"https://www.uvic.ca/calendar/undergrad/index.php#/experiences/BylJ9-cs4\">Faculty of Science</a> or the <a href=\"https://www.uvic.ca/calendar/undergrad/index.php#/experiences/Hk89awwsN?bc=true&amp;bcCurrent=%20Faculty%20of%20Social%20Sciences%3A%20Requirements&amp;bcGroup=Faculty%20of%20Social%20Sciences&amp;bcItemType=experiences\">Faculty of Social Sciences</a>.</p>",
